"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1931648-novak-djokovic-olympic-carlos-alcaraz\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Novak Djokovichas admitted he's on the lookout for revenge when he meetsCarlos Alcarazin theOlympicsingles final.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 115, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Djokovic missed out on a record-equalling eighthWimbledontitle last month, having been schooled by Alcaraz in the final at the All England Club.\", \"from\": 117, \"to\": 261, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 216, \"end\": 223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2701214240524177e-15, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}, {\"begin\": 244, \"end\": 260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/All_England_Lawn_Tennis_and_Croquet_Club\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"All England Club\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/All_England_Lawn_Tennis_and_Croquet_Club\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/All_England_Lawn_Tennis_and_Croquet_Club\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alcaraz romped to a straight-set victory during the pair's mid-July encounter, while confirming back-to-back Wimbledon final victories over 24-time Grand Slam winner Djokovic.\", \"from\": 263, \"to\": 438, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 263, \"end\": 270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2701214240524177e-15, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}, {\"begin\": 429, \"end\": 437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999999834017, \"rank\": 1.658882384159712e-11, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Djokovic has vowed to go all out whenhe takes to court Philippe-Chatrier tomorrow afternoonfor the Paris 2024 gold medal match against Alcaraz.\", \"from\": 440, \"to\": 587, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 444, \"end\": 452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999999834017, \"rank\": 1.658882384159712e-11, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 499, \"end\": 516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippe_Chatrier\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Philippe-Chatrier\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippe_Chatrier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippe_Chatrier\"}, {\"begin\": 543, \"end\": 553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999249667, \"rank\": 7.511608192820123e-11, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 579, \"end\": 586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2701214240524177e-15, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking after his semi-final victory over Lorenzo Musetti, Djokovic said: \\\"Although we played once [here], I beat him in the semis, I lost to him in the final of Wimbledon quite comfortably.\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 780, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 632, \"end\": 647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorenzo_Musetti\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lorenzo Musetti\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorenzo_Musetti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorenzo_Musetti\"}, {\"begin\": 649, \"end\": 657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999999834017, \"rank\": 1.658882384159712e-11, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Different surface\\u2026 I feel like I am playing and moving better than I did at Wimbledon, so hopefully I will come out and play my best tennis and in a way, I have nothing to lose as I have already secured a medal, so I am going to go for it.\\\"\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 1023, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is an added pressure on Djokovic heading into the gold medal match, given the 37-year-old has never topped the podium at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1055, \"end\": 1063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999999834017, \"rank\": 1.658882384159712e-11, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Making his debut at the Beijing Games 14 years ago, Djokovic does boast an Olympic medal, but only a bronze one - something he's keen to change this weekend.\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1324, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1219, \"end\": 1227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999999834017, \"rank\": 1.658882384159712e-11, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1430, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1461, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  He added: \\\"It was such a tense match [against Musetti], a lot of emotions.\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1560, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So much expectation and stress coming into today's match, particularly [trying] to secure a medal for my country.\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1674, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A first final of the Olympics for me [so] I am thrilled.\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1733, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Obviously I want to win the gold, in a few days' time.\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1788, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am going to do my best to do that, but already this is a huge result for me under these circumstances and I was very nervous today, and before the match, I lost three out of four semi-finals of the Olympic Games that I have played in my career, so I really wanted to get through this hurdle.\\\"\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 2085, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pick up your ultimate guide to the Olympics!\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2131, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Going for Gold provides the day-by-day rundown of what's on and when.\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2201, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clickhereto buy.\", \"from\": 2202, \"to\": 2218, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Remarkably, Djokovic enters the clash as the underdog, with Alcaraz the form player heading into Sunday's match as the form player.\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2282, \"end\": 2289, \"title\": \"http://db